{"word":"G4790 - συγκοινωνέω - synkoinōnéō - soong-koy-no-neh'-o - Communicate with","slug":"G4790","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συγκοινωνέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>synkoinōnéō"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>soong-koy-no-neh'-o"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Communicate with"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x03C3;&#x03C5;&#x03B3;&#x03BA;&#x03BF;&#x03B9;&#x03BD;&#x03C9;&#x03BD;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03C9; - sugkoino&#x0304;neo&#x0304;</b> - <i>soong-koy-no-neh'-o</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/G4862\">G4862</a> and <a href=\"#/G2841\">G2841</a>; to <i>share</i> in company <i>with</i>, that is, <i>co-participate</i> in: - communicate (have fellowship) with, be partaker of."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/G2839\">G2839</a>, <a href=\"#/G2840\">G2840</a>, <a href=\"#/G2841\">G2841</a>, <a href=\"#/G2842\">G2842</a>, <a href=\"#/G2843\">G2843</a>, <a href=\"#/G2844\">G2844</a>, <a href=\"#/G4791\">G4791</a>"}]}